  "time_ut": 1660938258,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'National security essential for international investment'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "National security is paramount for the development and social structure of the country. Defense Secretary Kamal Gunaratne said that no investor would come forward to make investments in any country without national security.",
        "He said the above while addressing a meeting held yesterday (19) at the Government Information Department regarding media reporting on national security and law.",
        "Whether it is an underdeveloped country, a developing country, or a developed country, national security is very necessary if the country is to move forward. There is nothing to discuss. He said that any country that does not have national security will not move forward and said that no investor will come forward to make investments in any country that does not have national security.",
        "No country is going to come forward so easily to provide assistance and cooperation to a country that does not ensure national security because the way of life of its people is not progressing. The Defense Secretary said that as far as Sri Lanka is concerned, national security should be the backbone of the country.",
        "All agencies responsible for national security must march together, otherwise a crisis situation will emerge. Moreover, forest law cannot solve the problems. When arresting people who instigate violence, attack the police, criticize and fight with inappropriate words, lawyers come forward to save them. Not only that, they clapped their hands inside the court to support the protestors. Such a situation has arisen. But on the other hand, he said, the mental state of the assaulted police should be considered."
      ],
